{"title":"人在旅途——兼致李素丽","authors":["宋曙光"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":12,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在旅途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——兼致李素丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从朝阳升起的黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到夜幕降临的夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京宽阔的长街上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往返着不倦的车轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是在哪一辆车上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请告诉我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你今天值中班还是早班"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星熟悉你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路灯熟悉你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为你总是行色匆忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像乘客熟悉你一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年幼的叫你阿姨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年长的唤你闺女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下车人去远，声留情牵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你让自己的这辆车厢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿行在扑面的春风里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天热有话的凉爽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天有情的温暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季氤氲着真情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使每一个见过你的乘客"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重见雷锋的笑脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人你主动搀扶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲者你上前指点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的一双眼和两只手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既能帮助孤寡和陌生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又能震慑愚蛮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要在这有限的客车里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品味劳动者的全部内涵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘客能够逢站下车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你却甘愿没有终点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人若在旅途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都希望能与你为伴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感受生活的朴素与美丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为你选择的是一张通票"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面只有人生的起点"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}